              "text": "I convinced my friends that everything’s alright,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That my life and future and everything’s so bright."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But a sense inside me, my friends, I can’t deny,"
