      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh God, where are You? I need You desperately!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh God, who are You? Why don’t You answer me?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The heavens declare You and the earth shows Your beauty."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But I’m a man. Oh God, I’m so empty!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, have mercy! I’m crying for You!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Please hear! Are you really true?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’m dark and lonely. You’re far, far from me."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh Lord, I need You desperately!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "One day a friend told me that Jesus is the Lord."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To my great surprise, it’s written in the Word."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They asked me to believe You. Your name I once blasphemed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Dear Lord, You saved me just by calling on Your name."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, Lord Jesus, dear Son, so glorious,"
